					<h2 style="text-align: center;">BwC Schools Closed Due to COVID-19</h2>
<p><img class="aligncenter wp-image-2458 size-medium" src="https://beginningwithchildren.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/BWC_Badge_RGB-300x300.png" alt="" width="300" height="300" srcset="https://beginningwithchildren.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/BWC_Badge_RGB-300x300.png 300w, https://beginningwithchildren.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/BWC_Badge_RGB-150x150.png 150w, https://beginningwithchildren.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/BWC_Badge_RGB-768x768.png 768w, https://beginningwithchildren.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/BWC_Badge_RGB.png 976w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px"></p>
